{"tid":2446251,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"全港首個 港鐵站上蓋公營街市 27年開幕","createTime":"2021-03-14T10:08:18.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-15T00:10:57.000Z","uid":47352,"like":13,"dislike":104,"uniUserReply":76,"replies":[{"pid":"c7c0d14ea2275a1bb8a7af1028fe927f4cf58904","tid":2446251,"uid":47352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T10:08:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WxFTNqs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWxFTNqs.jpg&h=a5c2b02c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U9RLDxe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU9RLDxe.jpg&h=3ec9d19c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【天水圍公營街市預設151個攤位 頂樓建園景花園】<br />\n建築署向城規會申請，在天水圍西鐵站對出的天福路興建新街市，街市樓高3層，預計提供約151個檔位，包括水耕檔位、多個樓層戶外設園景花園。<br />\n<br />\n資料顯示政府當時預計街市在2023年動工、2027年上半年完工，工程費用預計高達12億港元。<br />\n<br />\n公眾可在4月7日前提出意見<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/tpb/tc/plan_application/A_TSW_75.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Ftpb%2Ftc%2Fplan_application%2FA_TSW_75.html&d=wSR7%2FpLLUFbraZn9MQiPfANVisxpnNpADW7ISUiLTyw%3D&h=67efa120\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/tpb/tc/plan_application/A_TSW_75.html</a>"},{"pid":"bdd9b5ba6e7a94f4eb0a792528771108c95a0871","tid":2446251,"uid":365765,"like":281,"dislike":1,"score":280,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T10:09:57.000Z","msg":"預見到西鐵有鼠周圍行<br />\n然後朝早多人到踩死晒啲老鼠<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f65c0aaffe6902c5c08a14f34262076045ed5813","tid":2446251,"uid":292796,"like":65,"dislike":1,"score":64,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T10:11:24.000Z","msg":"天水圍係咁起街市<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf9aad8893c5a6984c2012826807adaf122541ba","tid":2446251,"uid":56097,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T10:12:02.000Z","msg":"不多於8000中文字或英文字母(包括空格)"},{"pid":"8786b5e67ca636d48502888489bb5990f6a3fe8a",